name: Dark Horse
details:
Fuzz DistortionThe Dark Horse is a super-versatile silicon fuzz. This pedal covers a ton of ground for guitar and bass players from cool lo-fi tones to all out saturated, high-gain fuzz.
• Wide fuzz/gain range
• Volume, Treble, Sustain (gain) controls
• Retains low end for use with bass guitar
• Standard 9VDC power
• True bypass switching
